    <item>
      <title>非洲部长计划寻求改革全球金融秩序</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/african-ministers-to-seek-revamp-of-global-financial-system</link>
      <description><![CDATA[非洲各国财长计划呼吁对全球金融体系进行彻底改革，以更好地适应面临高债务、气候冲击加剧和通胀飙升的非洲大陆。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/african-ministers-to-seek-revamp-of-global-financial-system</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 14:32:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根士丹利的卡伦表示，债券多头正在投降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-28/bond-bulls-are-capitulating-morgan-stanley-s-caron-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利投资管理投资组合解决方案集团首席信息官 Jim Caron 表示，债券利率多头正在投降，10 年期国债收益率有可能升至 4.5%-4.6% 左右。他在接受“彭博公开赛”采访时发表讲话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-28/bond-bulls-are-capitulating-morgan-stanley-s-caron-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 14:30:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伯克希尔和礼来公司竞相动摇科技对万亿美元俱乐部的控制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/berkshire-brk-b-lilly-lly-race-to-shake-tech-s-grip-on-trillion-dollar-club</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大型科技股创造了美国万亿美元俱乐部，并且迄今为止一直占据主导地位。这是第一次，一场等待外来者加入他们行列的竞赛正在酝酿之中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/berkshire-brk-b-lilly-lly-race-to-shake-tech-s-grip-on-trillion-dollar-club</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 12:38:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>资本市场超出预期，加拿大皇家银行超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/rbc-tops-estimates-as-capital-markets-outperform-expectations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大皇家银行超出了分析师的预期，因为该公司资本市场和财富管理业务的表现强于预期，抵消了贷款损失准备金的增加和费用的增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/rbc-tops-estimates-as-capital-markets-outperform-expectations</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 11:27:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Klarna 声称人工智能正在替代客服人员的工作，呼叫中心公司陷入困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/teleperformance-sinks-as-klarna-fuels-worries-over-impact-of-ai</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞典金融科技公司 Klarna 发表声明，再次引发人们对人工智能将损害这家法国公司呼叫中心业务的担忧后，Teleperformance SE 股价周三暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/teleperformance-sinks-as-klarna-fuels-worries-over-impact-of-ai</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 10:58:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国要求宽客逐步取消被认为引发动荡的策略</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/china-tells-quant-funds-to-phase-out-strategy-blamed-for-turmoil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，中国监管机构正在采取措施，逐步缩小流行的量化交易策略的规模，该策略导致了本月中国股市的动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/china-tells-quant-funds-to-phase-out-strategy-blamed-for-turmoil</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 06:39:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国库存增加，石油价格上涨，OPEC+供应政策成为焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-27/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-28</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价上涨，扭转了早前的跌势，因为美国原油库存的预期增加被欧佩克+将延长减产的预期所掩盖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-27/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-28</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 23:25:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
